<H3> <TI>   Czech Defense Ministry Delegation Arrives </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1701140294 Vilnius Radio Vilnius Network in Lithuanian 
1200 GMT 17 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1701140294 </F>
<F P=104>  Vilnius Radio Vilnius Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Lithuanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A Czech Defense Ministry delegation, headed by 
Defense Minister Antonin Baudys, has arrived in Vilnius for a 
three-day visit. 
  The guests have already met National Defense Minister Linas 
Linkevicius. This afternoon the delegation from the Czech 
Defense Ministry will be received by Algirdas Brazauskas, the 
president of the Republic of Lithuania, and Seimas Chairman 
