<F P=100> RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Political Issues </F>
<H3> <TI>   Government Meeting Postponed Due To Ongoing Reshuffle </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1801092094 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0739 GMT 18 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1801092094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Oleg Velichko] </F>
  [Text] Moscow January 18 TASS -- The Russian government 
postponed a meeting scheduled for Tuesday [18 January] because 
reshuffling of the government has not yet been completed, TASS 
learned from government administration. 
  The meeting was to discuss the situation in the aluminum- 
producing industry and export quotas for 1994. 

</TEXT>

