<F P=102>  LD1801112194 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Russian 
1000 GMT 18 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1801112194 </F>
<F P=104>  Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The car of Colonel Nurali Sheraliyev, deputy defense 
minister of the republic, was fire upon by unknown gunmen 
yesterday evening. 
  Sheraliyev was returning to Dushanbe from the town of Nurek 
[80km south-east of Dushanbe]. 
  The driver was killed and Colonel Sheraliyev and another 
person in the car were wounded as a result of the armed attack 
which took place between the towns of Nurek and Kofarnihon [25km 
south-east of Dushanbe]. 
  The competent bodies have begun an investigation of the 
case. 
This was told to a correspondent of Khovar news agency by the 
reliable sources. 

</TEXT>

